Architecture: all
Description: Metapackage to fulfill some hard dependencies of raspberrypi-sys-mods
 This metapackage provides a few packages needed by Raspberry Pi
 Foundation's raspberrypi-sys-mods and other Raspberry Pi Foundation
 provided metapackages for Raspbian to allow installation of
 alternatives for the same functionality or to rip out useless stuff
 like non-current gcc-*base.
 .
 It also conflicts with packages, Axel doesn't want to see on any of
 his Raspberry Pis. These conflicts are currently meant for Raspbian
 10 Buster.
 .
 Additionally it functions as metapackage for all the relevant non-GUI
 packages from the Raspberry Pi Foundation.
 .
 It won't be installable on any other OS than the Raspberry Pi
 Foundation's Raspbian images..

